en: Haven't seen you around here before.
Really? I've been here for YEARS.
Oh nice, how do you like it so far?
No way. I knew I shouldn't have stopped taking my pills.
Well, my name is Joey. You can call me Joe, J, Bob.  Whatever you want really.
I've run the one and only fishing shop in this whole town.
So come on down when you want to take a little swim.
Swim? I thought you're a fishing shop?
